at Saks have commonly blamed return fraud, exacerbated by an automated ware=
house process=E2=80=94i.e.,
if someone sends back a can of tuna in place of a Dolce & Gabbana ashtray, =
the next person who buys that Dolce & Gabbana ashtray will unfortunately re=
